commit.message:
Enabled use of custom-controls on checkbox inputs when show_form_labels is False (#25)

* Update field.html to enable the use of custom-controls on checkbox inputs when show_form_labels is False (#1)

The current code prevents the display of checkboxes (single) as BS4 custom-controls if show_form_labels is False.
This modification moves the control of the label display around the label block itself allowing the display of checkboxes as custom-control regardless of the value of show_form_labels.

commit.message:
Updated support Django versions (#21)

* Dropped support for Django 3.2, 4.0 and 4.1.
* Added support for Django 5.0.

With support for Django 3.2 being removed, the minimum supported Python version is now increased to 3.8.

Also speedup tox by building a wheel and sharing across tox environments. See https://hynek.me/articles/turbo-charge-tox/
